@startuml
title GoF Pattern : Observer + Strategy

note as GoFLabel
  **<<Observer + Strategy>>**
end note

class Account {
  + balance: float
  + riskLevel: int
  + updateBalance(): void
}
class RiskManagementModule {
  - account: Account
  - notifyAccountChanges(): void
}
class FraudDetectionService {
  - account: Account
  - detectFraud(): void
}
class CustomerNotificationService {
  - account: Account
  - sendNotifications(): void
}
interface AccountBalanceObserver {
  + updateAccountBalance(account: Account): void
}
class Strategy {
  - account: Account
  - execute(): void
}

Account --> RiskManagementModule
Account --> FraudDetectionService
Account --> CustomerNotificationService
RiskManagementModule ..> Strategy
FraudDetectionService ..> Strategy
CustomerNotificationService ..> Strategy
GoFLabel .. Account
@enduml